Privacy Policy
Privacy Policy
日本語 >>
Megasoft Inc. ("Megasoft") respects your privacy. Please read the following to learn more about our Privacy Policy ("this Policy").
< Effective Date : 8/8/2024 >
Use Your Personal Data
We may use your personal data for the following purposes:
When we provide you services and supports.
When we process your payment, deliver the products or services that you purchased.
When we send newsletters about your products and services.
When we reply to your inquiry.
When collect the statistics about our product (excluding your personal information).
When it is necessary to use within the scope of the purpose of utilization.
Disclose Personal Data
We do not sell, lease, rent or otherwise disclose your personal data to third parties unless otherwise your permission or stated below.
When services are provided by partners authorized by Megasoft. For example, when you make an online purchase from Megasoft, we must share your personal data with the logistics provider to arrange shipment or a partner to provide services.
To comply with applicable laws or respond to valid legal procedures, Megasoft may also disclose your personal data to law enforcement or other government agencies. With your request, your personal data may be also disclosed when appropriate, for example, to execute Terms and Conditions, when we believe disclosure is necessary.
Security
We take precautions to protect your information. When you submit sensitive information via the website, your information is protected both online and offline.
We take precautions to prevent from unjust access to personal information, disappearance, manipulation, a leak does not happen.
Cookies
Megasoft uses cookies to operate and improve our websites and offerings.
Usage of cookies is in no way linked to any personally identifiable information on our site.
You can disable cookies by your browser setting.
Some of the services on our website may not be functioned, when cookies are set to disable.
When you login to our Services
For statistics purpose, we collect the following information when you log in our service.
Your domain name, IP address, browser, access date (Not your private information included).
Secure Sockets Layer (SSL)
Megasoft use the Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) protocol, which encrypts any personal information you enter into registration forms on the application.
The encryption process protects your information, by scrambling it before it is sent to us from your computer. We also make commercially reasonable effort to ensure the security of your personal information on our system.
(We try striving to protect your personal information.)
About products with Google Drive integration functions
< 3D My Home Designer Series >
For applications that implement a function to upload data to Google Drive using Google API, the customer can connect to Google Drive from this application and save the created data to the PC, and then upload the same data to Google Drive. The same data can be uploaded to Google Drive.
This application does not perform any operations other than uploading data.
It does not connect to your Google Drive for any purposes other than those described above.
The use of information received from the Google API and its transfer to other applications is governed by
the user data policy of the Google API service
, including any restricted use requirements.
＜LiquidLogic＞
Using Google APIs to allow file and folder operations (view, create, delete, move, rename, upload, download) and edit files.
Communications are encrypted with SSL and login credentials are encrypted by iOS.
We do not retain any user information.
The use of information received from the Google API and its transfer to other applications is governed by
the user data policy of the Google API service
, including any restricted use requirements.
Modify and Cancellation
When you request to modify or delete your personal information or to cancel the services, Megasoft responds to your request promptly under our terms and conditions.
Changes to this Privacy Policy
Megasoft reserves the right to update or change this Policy at any time. We will release the latest Privacy Policy on our Website.
Contact
In matters pertaining to Megasoft's privacy practices you may contact via email at
：
privacy@megasoft.co.jp
